{"tid":1874441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本新增兩宗武漢肺炎病例 搭撤僑班機回國初期檢測為陰性","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T08:16:25.000Z","uid":60545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a19fcb5d5224824bf3b849f25af1b19ce6d821ba","tid":1874441,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"日本厚生勞動省宣布，1月底搭乘撤僑專機、從中國湖北省武漢市返國的僑民中，出現2名新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）確診病例，讓乘撤僑專機歸國的確診病例累計達12人。<br />\n<br />\n日媒報導，兩名確診病例分別為搭乘第一班專機的50多歲男子，以及搭乘第二班專機的40歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n《AbemaNEWS》指出，50多歲確診病例1月30日初次檢查呈現陰性反應，7日發燒到攝氏38.5度，因此二度採集檢體送驗，千葉縣衛生研究所檢查仍呈現陰性，改送日本國立感染症研究所檢查，這才出現陽性反應。據指男子回國和入住隔離用飯店後，就未曾離開房間。<br />\n<br />\n另1名確診病患1月30日回國後，就待在埼玉縣的家中，8日自行通報出現發燒症狀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/amp/story/5599/4336784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Famp%2Fstory%2F5599%2F4336784&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=f979ebac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/amp/story/5599/4336784</a>"},{"pid":"5bd8b2bb5dc6d077d4f5f23c30dca9609958f4f6","tid":1874441,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:04:34.000Z","msg":"奶共嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18270cd8bce6c37067ff0f436db2fa55a5a60a13","tid":1874441,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f64a2630075576a11db8c9d7f4a1662a1a3de1","tid":1874441,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"前日郵輪千幾個老陰落咗船"},{"pid":"cdb5f37bb7dac17dde4c1cb957ab380b0b9ff94b","tid":1874441,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"玩9人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdc37675c35ba456c27e4e4eba2092bda5ba7e5","tid":1874441,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5f64a2630075576a11db8c9d7f4a1662a1a3de1","tid":1874441,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"前日郵輪千幾個老陰落咗船"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:16:25.000Z","msg":"林鄭表示：我就係要呢啲.jpg"}]}